{
  "chapter": "035",
  "title": "管蔡世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "武王同母十兄弟",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔鲜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔度</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文王</span>的儿子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>的弟弟。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>同母<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十人</span>。母亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太姒</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>的正妃。其长子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯邑考</span>，其次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王发</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔鲜</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔度</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹叔振铎</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成叔武</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霍叔处</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔封</span>，再次是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季载</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季载</span>年纪最小。同母<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十人</span>，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">发</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">旦</span>贤能，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>左右辅佐，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>舍弃<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯邑考</span>而以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">发</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">发</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯邑考</span>此前已先去世。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "武王封建诸弟",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>攻克<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>以后，平定天下，分封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>和兄弟。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔鲜</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">管</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔度</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武庚禄父</span>，治理<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的遗民。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔旦</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>而在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>辅政，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔振铎</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔武</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">成</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔处</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔封</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季载</span>都年幼，未得封国。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "管蔡作乱与周公东征",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>去世后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>年幼，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>独掌<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">王室</span>政务。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔</span>怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>的做法不利于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>，便挟持<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武庚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">作乱</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>之命<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武庚</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔</span>，将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">放</span>逐，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">迁</span>徙之，给他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十乘</span>，随从<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十人</span>。把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的余民分为两部分：一部分<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微子启</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，以承续<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的祭祀；另一部分<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>君，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫康叔</span>。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季载</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">厓</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>都有善行，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司寇</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司空</span>，来辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>治理，都在天下有美名。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "蔡仲改行复封于蔡",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔度</span>迁徙后死去。他的儿子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡仲\">胡（蔡仲）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡仲\">胡（蔡仲）</span>改变操行，遵循德行、顺善而行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>听说后，举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡仲\">胡（蔡仲）</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿士</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国得以治理。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>进言，又将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡仲\">胡（蔡仲）</span>复<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，来奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔</span>的祭祀，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡仲</span>。其余五位叔辈都去就国，没有做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>官吏的。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "蔡国早期世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡仲</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡伯荒</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡伯荒</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宫侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宫侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武侯</span>在位时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉王</span>失国，奔逃至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">共和</span>行政，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>多叛离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "夷侯至釐侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣王</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">所事</span>即位。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "釐侯时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽王</span>被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">犬戎</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">室</span>衰微而东迁。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>开始得以列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "共侯至戴侯至宣侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兴</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戴侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戴侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">措父</span>即位。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "宣侯至哀侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>初立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">封人</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓侯</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡哀侯\">献舞（蔡哀侯）</span>即位。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "哀侯被楚所虏",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>。当初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span>娶<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>女，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">息侯</span>也娶<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>女。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">息夫人</span>将归宁，路过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>对她不敬。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">息侯</span>发怒，请<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>：\"来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我，我求救于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>必来救，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>趁机<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>之，可以取得战功。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>依计而行，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡哀侯</span>而归。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span>滞留<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>，死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。共在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>而卒。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>人立其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">肸</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "缪侯与齐桓公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span>将其妹嫁给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十八年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡女</span>在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>中嬉戏，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>摇<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>制止，不听，公大怒，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡女</span>遣送回国但未断绝关系。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>发怒，将其妹改嫁他人。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>发怒，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>溃败，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span>，南进至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邵陵</span>。不久<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>致歉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐侯</span>遣还<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">甲午</span>即位。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "庄侯至文侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城濮</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商臣</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其父<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>而代立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穆公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄王</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文侯申</span>即位。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "文侯时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏徵舒</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>又释放了它。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯固</span>即位。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "景侯被太子所弑",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄王</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯</span>为太子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">般</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>娶妇，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯</span>与儿媳私通。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵侯</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "灵侯被楚灵王诱杀",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">围</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郏敖</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">招</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀公</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃疾</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>而据有其地。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵王</span>以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵侯</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其父为由，诱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡灵侯</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">申</span>，埋伏甲士与他饮酒，乘其醉<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span>杀其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十人</span>。命公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃疾</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一月</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃疾</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">蔡公（楚平王）</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "楚平王复立蔡",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>三年后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃疾</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵王</span>而代立，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>于是寻求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡景侯</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庐</span>，立他为君，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span>。这一年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国也恢复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>刚即位，想亲近<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，所以恢复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>之后。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "悼侯至昭侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">般</span>之孙<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">东国</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span>之子而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼侯</span>父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐太子友</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐太子友</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵侯</span>的太子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span>即位后<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐太子</span>，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span>死后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐太子</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">东国</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平侯</span>之子而代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯申</span>即位。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "昭侯朝楚受辱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>，持美<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">裘</span>两件，把一件献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>，自己穿一件。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>想要此裘，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>不给。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>便在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王前谗毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>，使他滞留<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>察觉后，便把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">裘</span>献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>收受，于是进言放归<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>回国后前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，请求与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "迁州来与昭侯遇弑",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">春</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡昭侯</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵公</span>会于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邵陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯</span>私下结交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苌弘</span>以求序位高于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>让史官陈述<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>的功德，于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>的序位居先。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">沈</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>发怒，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡昭侯</span>使其子到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国作<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">质</span>，以共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">冬</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖闾</span>终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>恐惧，逃奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>离去而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>复国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>为其民众流泪以谋讨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡昭侯</span>恐惧。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>恐惧，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>告急。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>觉得<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>太远，约定<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">迁</span>到靠近吴国的地方，便于相救；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>私自允诺，没有与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>商议。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>人来救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，趁机将<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">迁</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">州来</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>将<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>恐怕他又再<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">迁</span>国，便命令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贼</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">利</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>；随后<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贼</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">利</span>以推卸罪责，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">朔</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成侯</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "成侯至楚灭蔡",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声侯产</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">元侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">元侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯齐</span>即位。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "楚灭蔡",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯齐</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡侯齐</span>出逃，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>从此祭祀断绝。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十三年（时长）</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "武王诸弟封国概况",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯邑考</span>，其后裔不知所封之国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王发</span>，其后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">本纪</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔鲜</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">作乱</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>死，无后。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>，其后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔度</span>，其后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹叔振铎</span>，其后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成叔武</span>，其后世不详。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霍叔处</span>，其后代在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">献公</span>时被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔封</span>，其后代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>，有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">世家</span>记述。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季载</span>，其后世不详。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "太史公论管蔡",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管叔鲜\">管（管叔鲜）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡叔度\">蔡（蔡叔度）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">作乱</span>，没有值得记载的事。然而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>年幼，天下心怀疑虑，全靠同母之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成叔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厓季</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十人</span>的辅佐，因此<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>最终尊奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝，所以把这些附在<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">世家</span>中记述。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "曹叔振铎受封",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹叔振铎</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>的弟弟。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>攻克<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>后，将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔振铎</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "曹国早期世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔振铎</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太伯脾</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太伯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲君平</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲君平</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宫伯侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宫伯侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝伯云</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝伯云</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷伯喜</span>即位。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "夷伯时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷伯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉王</span>奔逃至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "幽伯至戴伯至惠伯",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷伯</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽伯彊</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽伯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽伯</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戴伯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戴伯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣王</span>已即位三年。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戴伯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠伯兕</span>即位。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "惠伯时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠伯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽王</span>被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">犬戎</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，于是东迁，日益卑弱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>背叛它。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>开始列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "缪公至桓公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十六</span>年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠伯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石甫</span>即位，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公终生</span>即位。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "桓公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">华父督</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">殇公</span>，连同<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔父</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公夕姑</span>即位。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "庄公时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>开始称霸。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "釐公至共公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐公夷</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭公班</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，于是进至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">召陵</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭公</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共公襄</span>即位。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "晋文公伐曹虏共公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共公（曹共公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>。当初，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重耳</span>逃亡路经<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹君</span>对他无礼，想观看他的骈胁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐负羁</span>进谏，不听，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐负羁</span>私下与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重耳</span>交好。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重耳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共公（曹共公）</span>而归，下令军队不得进入<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐负羁</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>所居的街巷。有人劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>说：\"从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>会合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，复立异姓之国；如今君王<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>君，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>同姓之国，凭什么号令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>于是释放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共公（曹共公）</span>回国。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "文公至成公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共公（曹共公）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公寿</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣公彊</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十七年</span>去世，其弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公负刍</span>即位。"
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "成公至平公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公</span>而归，不久又释放。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾书</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中行偃</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程滑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武公胜</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">弃疾</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>其君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵王</span>代立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武公</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公午</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">是岁</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>都发生了火灾。"
    },
    "36": {
      "title": "悼公至声公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">囚</span>之；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>人立他的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">野</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span>死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，运回安葬。"
    },
    "37": {
      "title": "声公至靖公至伯阳",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平公</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声公</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">声公</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">露</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">隐公</span>代立，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靖公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靖公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span>即位。"
    },
    "38": {
      "title": "伯阳信用公孙彊",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>有人梦见众多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>立于社宫，商议要灭亡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>国；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹叔振铎</span>制止他们，请求等待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>出现，众人答应了。天明，这人在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>国寻求此人，没有找到。做梦者告诫他的儿子说：\"我死后，你若听到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>执政，一定要离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>国，不要沾染<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>国的祸患。\" 到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span>即位，喜好射猎之事。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>国的野人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>也喜好射猎，猎得白<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">雁</span>献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span>，并陈述射猎之道，趁机谈论政事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span>非常欢悦，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>受宠，任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司城</span>以主持政事。做梦者的儿子于是离开曹国。"
    },
    "39": {
      "title": "宋灭曹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹伯</span>陈说霸业之道。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹伯</span>采纳了他的主张，于是背叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>而挑衅<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>曹，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>人不救。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">执</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹伯阳</span>及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>带回国<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>之。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>从此断绝了祭祀。"
    },
    "40": {
      "title": "太史公论曹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我考察<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共公（曹共公）</span>不任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：釐负羁\">僖负羁（釐负羁）</span>，而乘轩的人竟有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百人</span>，可知唯德不建。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹叔振铎\">振铎（曹叔振铎）</span>托梦之事，难道不是想延续<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>的祭祀吗？而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙彊</span>不修德政，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹叔振铎\">叔铎（曹叔振铎）</span>的祭祀就此断绝了。"
    },
    "41": {
      "title": "全篇总赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>的弟弟，封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">管</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">周公（姬旦）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>职，流言因此作起。 诗人以\"狼跋\"喻其艰难，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">鸱鸮</span>以讨凶恶。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡仲\">胡（蔡仲）</span>能改行，恢复其封爵。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡哀侯\">献舞（蔡哀侯）</span>被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">执</span>，因<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">息</span>的礼薄之故。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡缪侯\">穆侯（蔡缪侯）</span>被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span>，起于荡舟戏谑。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹共公\">共（曹共公）</span>轻慢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：釐负羁\">负羁（釐负羁）</span>先已觉察。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹伯阳\">伯阳（曹伯阳）</span>梦社宫之告，基业倾覆于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹叔振铎\">振铎（曹叔振铎）</span>。"
    }
  }
}